PRETORIA, South Africa, August 27, 2018/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The National Council of Provinces (NCOP) invites members of the media to a briefing on Taking Parliament to the People which will be held in the Mangaung Metropolitan Municipality tomorrow.





Permanent delegates to the NCOP are, this week, revisiting the Free State to report back on progress made regarding undertakings taken during last yearâ€™s Taking Parliament to the People programme. This flagship programme of the NCOP brings together all three levels of government in one place to meet face to face with locals to identify challenges and find solutions. The visit is from 28 - 30 August and will focus on health services and related matters in Mangaung Metropolitan and municipalities in Xhariep District



The Media Briefing will be held as follows:



Date: 27 August 2017

